{"type": "article", "id": 17966, "title": "行星盆栽", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-24T07:20:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115204e4Ihq18rk5txXLW6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是俄罗斯设计师 Katerina Kopytina 带来的盆栽系列，她想象那些位于 Kuiper Belt （柯伊伯带）的矮行星，虽然不容易见到，却是真实存在的。每一个盆栽都代表一个行星，挂在一个闭合的轨道上。黑色的金属架子构成盆栽的吊架，形状有些夸张却充满了幻想色彩。<a href=\"http://katerinakopytina.com/#/project/408\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115202EDLJyqQMxpZKaoUl.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"716\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74583333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115203JyfweLh1bc9Zptvu.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"639\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115203SBATxJwQ80CHfczm.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115204sqQpWSgIwxyklT9N.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}